  Locus:
    Page: 348
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Pain
---
With proper understanding, the pain and the pleasure are the same. Both are
lessons. In such a light, pain becomes pain no more. One who understands
the world in the proper way will see the pain is there as a necessity,
something to be risen above.
